function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.1.7') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.1.7!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

// Files different: README.md
function writefile_1() {
	$fp = @fopen('README.md', 'w');
	if ($fp === false) {
		warn('File README.md cannot be written');
		return;
	}
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('IyBBYm91dCBPSURwbHVzIDIuMAoKIyMjIFdoYXQgaXMgT0lEcGx1cz8KT0lEcGx1cyBpcyBhbiBPcGVuU291cmNlIHNvZnR3YXJlIHNvbHV0aW9uIGJ5IFZpYVRoaW5rU29mdCB0aGF0IGNhbiBiZSB1c2VkIGJ5ClJlZ2lzdHJhdGlvbiBBdXRob3JpdGllcyB0byBt'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('YW5hZ2UgYW5kIHB1Ymxpc2ggaW5mb3JtYXRpb24gYWJvdXQKT2JqZWN0IElkZW50aWZpZXJzIChPSURzKSwgR2xvYmFsbHkgVW5pcXVlIElkZW50aWZpZXJzIChHVUlEcyksIGFuZCBtdWNoIG1vcmUuCgpNb3JlIGluZm9ybWF0aW9uIGFzIHdlbGwgYXMgYSBkZW1v'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('IHZlcnNpb24gb2YgT0lEcGx1cyBjYW4gYmUgZm91bmQgaGVyZToKaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cub2lkcGx1cy5jb20vCgojIyMgRG93bmxvYWQgYW5kIGluc3RhbGwgT0lEcGx1cwoKIyMjIyMgTWV0aG9kIEEgLSBEb3dubG9hZCB1c2luZyBTVk46CiAgICBzdWRvIGFwdC1n'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('ZXQgdXBkYXRlCiAgICBzdWRvIGFwdC1nZXQgaW5zdGFsbCBzdm4KICAgIHN2biBjbyBodHRwczovL3N2bi52aWF0aGlua3NvZnQuY29tL3N2bi9vaWRwbHVzL3RydW5rLwoKIyMjIyMgTWV0aG9kIEIgLSBEb3dubG9hZCB1c2luZyBHaXQ6CiAgICBzdWRvIGFwdC1n'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('ZXQgdXBkYXRlCiAgICBzdWRvIGFwdC1nZXQgaW5zdGFsbCBnaXQKICAgIGdpdCBjbG9uZSBodHRwczovL2dpdGh1Yi5jb20vZGFuaWVsbWFyc2NoYWxsL29pZHBsdXMuZ2l0CgojIyMjIyBNZXRob2QgQyAtIERvd25sb2FkIFNWTiBzbmFwc2hvdDoKRG93bmxvYWQg'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('YSBUQVIuR1ogZmlsZSBoZXJlOiBodHRwczovL29pZHBsdXMuY29tL2Rvd25sb2FkLnBocAoKIyMjIFN5c3RlbSByZXF1aXJlbWVudHMKLSBQSFAgY29tcGF0aWJsZSB3ZWIgc2VydmVyICh0ZXN0ZWQgd2l0aCBBcGFjaGUgMiwgbmdpbngsIGFuZCBNaWNyb3NvZnQg'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('SUlTKQotIFBIUCA3LjAgb3IgaGlnaGVyICh0ZXN0ZWQgdGlsbCBQSFAgdmVyc2lvbiA4LjMgaW5jbHVzaXZlKQogICAgICAgIHdpdGggZXh0ZW5zaW9uIE15U1FMaSwgUG9zdGdyZVNRTCwgU1FMaXRlMywgUERPLCBPQ0k4LCBvciBPREJDLCBkZXBlbmRpbmcgb24g'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('eW91ciBkYXRhYmFzZQotIFN1cHBvcnRlZCBkYXRhYmFzZXM6CiAgICAgICAgTXlTUUwvTWFyaWFEQiwKICAgICAgICBQb3N0Z3JlU1FMLAogICAgICAgIFNRTGl0ZTMsCiAgICAgICAgTWljcm9zb2Z0IFNRTCBTZXJ2ZXIsCiAgICAgICAgT3JhY2xlLAogICAgICAg'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('IE1pY3Jvc29mdCBBY2Nlc3MsCiAgICAgICAgRmlyZWJpcmQKLSBJbmRlcGVuZGVudCBvZiBvcGVyYXRpbmcgc3lzdGVtcyAodGVzdGVkIHdpdGggV2luZG93cywgTGludXggYW5kIG1hY09TIFgpCgojIyMgUmVwb3J0aW5nIGEgYnVnCllvdSBjYW4gZmlsZSBhIGJ1'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('ZyByZXBvcnQgaGVyZToKLSBodHRwczovL2dpdGh1Yi5jb20vZGFuaWVsbWFyc2NoYWxsL29pZHBsdXMvaXNzdWVzIChyZWNvbW1lbmRlZCkKLSBodHRwczovL3d3dy52aWF0aGlua3NvZnQuY29tL2NvbnRhY3QvZGFuaWVsLW1hcnNjaGFsbCAoZm9yIGNvbmZpZGVu'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('dGlhbCByZXBvcnRzKQoKIyMjIFN1cHBvcnQKSWYgeW91IGhhdmUgYW55IHF1ZXN0aW9ucyBvciBuZWVkIGhlbHAsIHBsZWFzZSBjb250YWN0IHVzOgpodHRwczovL3d3dy52aWF0aGlua3NvZnQuY29tL2NvbnRhY3QvZGFuaWVsLW1hcnNjaGFsbAo='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('README.md')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: README.md');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('README.md')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): README.md');
	} else if (sha1_file('README.md') != 'ad1b156c71aef42fbd5fa2363e9e25add38dbcde') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): README.md');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('README.md', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of README.md');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('README.md') !== 'ad1b156c71aef42fbd5fa2363e9e25add38dbcde') {
		if (@sha1_file('README.md') !== 'cb79e0f7e470d4c935dbe7b4724e52d79d06ef12') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: README.md');
			$tmp = pathinfo('README.md');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('README.md')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('README.md', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('README.md') !== 'ad1b156c71aef42fbd5fa2363e9e25add38dbcde') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): README.md');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('TODO')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: TODO');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('TODO')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): TODO');
	} else if (sha1_file('TODO') != 'a62480c18395eb4c4915cbed68f7e0257d099adb') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): TODO');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('TODO', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of TODO');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'a62480c18395eb4c4915cbed68f7e0257d099adb') {
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '19a4bebe34af1f13c7ea417e5a10634dcaed4c37') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'a62480c18395eb4c4915cbed68f7e0257d099adb') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: changelog.json.php');
	writefile_3();
	if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): changelog.json.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('changelog.json.php') != '3c8a2e60d507ceda85844e4c7837f7eb11f162ee') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('changelog.json.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of changelog.json.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '3c8a2e60d507ceda85844e4c7837f7eb11f162ee') {
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '0f8ab55d872b365ff53d2f68a29cac42e3bbe59b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: changelog.json.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('changelog.json.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('changelog.json.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('changelog.json.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_3();
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '3c8a2e60d507ceda85844e4c7837f7eb11f162ee') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
		}
	}
}

			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');

if (!is_file('doc/faq.md')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/faq.md');
	writefile_8();
	if (!is_file('doc/faq.md')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/faq.md');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/faq.md') != 'ef4ccaba9d4252dcf81bafb3ce247e8e0fd1d507') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/faq.md');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/faq.md', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/faq.md');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/faq.md') !== 'ef4ccaba9d4252dcf81bafb3ce247e8e0fd1d507') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/faq.md') !== 'fb16342461eb0985f113bb7b479003c4ddb741de') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/faq.md');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/faq.md');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/faq.md')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/faq.md', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_8();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/faq.md') !== 'ef4ccaba9d4252dcf81bafb3ce247e8e0fd1d507') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/faq.md');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/website/download.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/website/download.html');
	writefile_9();
	if (!is_file('doc/website/download.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/website/download.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/website/download.html') != '8e818b4913c66c58edc736b0cfe715784ef11495') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/website/download.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/website/download.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/website/download.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/website/download.html') !== '8e818b4913c66c58edc736b0cfe715784ef11495') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/download.html') !== '7b0d34e78f616ce1e9e4f0cfa8f22509fd5df3d8') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/website/download.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/website/download.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/website/download.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/website/download.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_9();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/download.html') !== '8e818b4913c66c58edc736b0cfe715784ef11495') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/website/download.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/website/examples.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/website/examples.html');
	writefile_10();
	if (!is_file('doc/website/examples.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/website/examples.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/website/examples.html') != '817263eb62fab3890c859b9ca6b470b832bb309c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/website/examples.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/website/examples.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/website/examples.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/website/examples.html') !== '817263eb62fab3890c859b9ca6b470b832bb309c') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/examples.html') !== '0002393bc7e381fd9092f1bea91751e59d9110b9') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/website/examples.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/website/examples.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/website/examples.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/website/examples.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/examples.html') !== '817263eb62fab3890c859b9ca6b470b832bb309c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/website/examples.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/website/support.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/website/support.html');
	writefile_11();
	if (!is_file('doc/website/support.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/website/support.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/website/support.html') != 'b125ca373e2397853c178ec1c7957d86f1bd2102') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/website/support.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/website/support.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/website/support.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/website/support.html') !== 'b125ca373e2397853c178ec1c7957d86f1bd2102') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/support.html') !== '5b1dcc21b08c3e93637a4d6c946fe319300105b5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/website/support.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/website/support.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/website/support.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/website/support.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/website/support.html') !== 'b125ca373e2397853c178ec1c7957d86f1bd2102') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/website/support.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml');
	writefile_52();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml') != '48eec8e8df151064881d7ff05546b6ede94596bf') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml') !== '48eec8e8df151064881d7ff05546b6ede94596bf') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml') !== 'e46ca6b99a40067f8dc9094edf390894d67d370c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_52();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml') !== '48eec8e8df151064881d7ff05546b6ede94596bf') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/database/pgsql/manifest.xml');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	writefile_120();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') != '4182de38eb9b48b7b981da6c17fb8a8cdc4d22d3') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') !== '4182de38eb9b48b7b981da6c17fb8a8cdc4d22d3') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') !== '34742deb107c58146ff19201a2965b10b4ced76f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_120();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') !== '4182de38eb9b48b7b981da6c17fb8a8cdc4d22d3') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.json');
	writefile_124();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') != 'dedeaeae9c0b1f490637c7961a1c887ffbf357d7') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== 'dedeaeae9c0b1f490637c7961a1c887ffbf357d7') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== 'b3e96a5074d68015f06dd3e565d9d1661a855068') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_124();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== 'dedeaeae9c0b1f490637c7961a1c887ffbf357d7') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.php');
	writefile_125();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') != '0386d01a135f89985ca9ac00392a6346cec8c530') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== '0386d01a135f89985ca9ac00392a6346cec8c530') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== '34d82caed7624377dba2ede606eb3f7d9facc3a6') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_125();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== '0386d01a135f89985ca9ac00392a6346cec8c530') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
		}
	}
}

		}
	}
}
